{"tid":25831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉工討論】空少定社工","createTime":"2016-12-06T11:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T11:13:13.000Z","uid":57971,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e134a6c028b8c3507f6e9df2562ec272af1d29c7","tid":25831,"uid":57971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，小弟第一次係道開post，有錯麻煩屌得細力啲，鍚住我個菊花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都知尼2個職業都係高登仔最憎ge，但小弟真心求賜教<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟上年asso社工grad左之後去左做空少，而家飛左年幾，我飛得都算多，每個月人工大約得兩萬左右，少過高登仔好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飛左年幾其實我都仲幾中意呢份工，好多假期又好輕鬆，無憂無慮，但奈何小弟家貧要養家，喱道每年人工加得幾百，眼見以前d同學人工愈來愈高，好有衝動想番番去做社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然我做社工同空少ge ceiling都係差唔多，都係35k咁上下，但社工會快d同穩定d上到ceiling，但同時working load同壓力都會幾何級咁上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全能高登仔求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da9a70c06c58772ec15d5bb7c02c8249b777615","tid":25831,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"尼你老母"},{"pid":"bb601f9ff122982aa79b9ddc668d5b0b646d5836","tid":25831,"uid":57971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尼你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對唔住大佬，第一次開post一時打錯<br />\n插細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj